This paper is about multi-domain image-to-image translation, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for this task, which involves using relative attributes, which could be considered a machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) technique. Additionally, the paper includes experimental results, which could also place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) or graphics (cs.GR) categories.
